trans-unit.source: Provides module initialization and disposal events to the implementing class.
trans-unit.target: 提供給實作的類別模組初始化和處置事件。

trans-unit.source: Disposes of the resources (other than memory) used by the module that implements <xref href="System.Web.IHttpModule"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 處置模組實作使用的資源 （除了記憶體之外） <xref href="System.Web.IHttpModule"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method performs any final cleanup work prior to removal of the module from the execution pipeline.
trans-unit.target: Dispose 方法會從執行管線執行之前移除模組的任何最後的清除工作。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a module and prepares it to handle requests.
trans-unit.target: 初始化模組，並準備好處理要求。

trans-unit.source: Use the Init method to register event handling methods with specific events.
trans-unit.target: 使用 Init 方法來註冊事件處理方法向特定事件。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication"></xref> that provides access to the methods, properties, and events common to all application objects within an ASP.NET application
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication"> </xref>可提供存取的方法、 屬性和 ASP.NET 應用程式中的所有應用程式物件通用的事件
